类 CachedAuthProvider

  • 所有已实现的接口:
    AylaAuthProvider

    public class CachedAuthProvider
extends BaseAuthProvider
    AylaAuthProvider that uses cached credentials to sign in. If your application is saving the AylaAuthorization to log the user in automatically on subsequent runs of the app, this object can be initialized with the cached credentials and passed to AylaLoginManager.signIn(AylaAuthProvider, String, Response.Listener, ErrorListener) to sign-in the user.

    The CachedAuthProvider will refresh the provided credentials as part of the sign-in process if the cloud is available.

    This class allows for offline sign-in if the cloud service is available. If the cloud service is not available, and the object was initialized with allowOfflineLogin set to true, the provider will allow the sign-in operation to succeed.

    While the cloud service is unavailable, the system will attempt to return cached data to API requests whenever possible. Not all data is cached, however, so the application should always be prepared to receive error responses to any API request.

      • getCachedProvider

        public static CachedAuthProvider getCachedProvider(android.content.Context context)
        Returns a CachedAuthProvider initialized with credentials that have been cached via a call to cacheAuthorization(Context, AylaAuthorization).
        参数:
        context - Context used to obtain shared preferences to obtain the cached data
        返回:
        A CachedAuthProvider object initialized with the cached authorization, or null if no cached authorization data was found.

      • cacheAuthorization

        public static void cacheAuthorization(android.content.Context context,
                                      AylaAuthorization authorization)
        Saves the provided authorization object to cache. CachedAuthProvider objects initialized with this cached authorization may be created via a call to (Context, boolean).
        参数:
        context - Context used to obtain shared preferences to store the cached data
        authorization - Authorization object to be cached

      • clearCachedAuthorization

        public static void clearCachedAuthorization(android.content.Context context)
        Clears cached authorization. This method should be called whenever the user signs out if the application uses cached authorization.
        参数:
        context - Context used to obtain shared preferences to clear the cached data

      • authenticate

        public void authenticate(AylaAuthProvider.AuthProviderListener listener)
        从接口复制的说明: AylaAuthProvider
        Called by AylaLoginManager, this method should perform the necessary operations to sign in a user. On successful sign-in, the method should call the provided listener via didAuthenticate and provide the AylaAuthorization object with the necessary authenticated credentials. This method should only be called by AylaLoginManager.
        参数:
        listener - The listener to be notified of sign-in success or failure.

      • authenticate

        public void authenticate(AylaAuthProvider.AuthProviderListener listener,
                         java.lang.String sessionName)
        从接口复制的说明: AylaAuthProvider
        Called by AylaLoginManager, this method should perform the necessary operations to sign in a user. On successful sign-in, the method should call the provided listener via didAuthenticate and provide the AylaAuthorization object with the necessary authenticated credentials.
        参数:
        listener - The listener to be notified of sign-in success or failure.
        sessionName - Name of the session for which this authentication is done. This is used for offline mode login
